sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as SkillChat Component
    participant API as Express Server
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant LLM as LLM Provider API

    U->>FE: Enter use-case description
    FE->>API: POST /api/chat
    Note right of FE: Body: {message, skillCode, evaluationSummary, conversationHistory}

    API->>DB: SELECT FROM provider_configs
    DB-->>API: Provider config (provider, apiKey, model)

    alt No Provider Configured
        API-->>FE: 400 {message: "No AI provider configured", needsConfig: true}
        FE->>U: Show "Configure AI Provider" prompt
    end

    API->>API: Build system prompt
    Note over API: System prompt bundles:<br/>1. Role definition<br/>2. JSON response format<br/>3. Skill code<br/>4. Evaluation summary<br/>5. Conversation history

    alt OpenAI
        API->>LLM: POST api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions
    else Anthropic
        API->>LLM: POST api.anthropic.com/v1/messages
    else AI Foundry
        API->>LLM: POST {targetUri}/chat/completions
    else GCP Vertex AI
        API->>LLM: POST {region}-aiplatform.googleapis.com/v1/...
    else AWS Bedrock
        API->>LLM: POST bedrock-runtime.{region}.amazonaws.com/...
    end

    LLM-->>API: LLM response text

    API->>API: Parse JSON from response
    Note over API: Expected: {fit, feedback, report, refinedCode}

    alt Valid JSON
        API-->>FE: {fit, feedback, report, refinedCode}
    else Invalid JSON
        API->>API: Fallback: wrap raw text
        API-->>FE: {fit: "Unknown", feedback: raw text, report: raw text}
    end

    FE->>FE: Render structured response
    FE->>U: Display fitness badge, feedback, report, refined code
